queryLines: -- cohort builder for Pixels Dashboard with base ( SELECT meta:['0020000D'].Value[0] StudyInstanceUID, meta:['00081030'].Value[0] StudyDescription, meta:['0020000E'].Value[0] SeriesInstanceUID, meta:['0008103E'].Value[0] SeriesDescription, meta:['00200010'].Value[0] StudyID, -- meta:['00200011'].Value[0] SeriesNumber, -- meta:['00200013'].Value[0] InstanceNumber, meta:['00100010'].Value[0].Alphabetic as PatientName, meta:['00100020'].Value[0] PatientID, try_cast(try_to_timestamp(meta:['00100030'].Value[0],"yyyyMMdd") as Date) as PatientBirthDate, try_cast(left(meta:['00101010'].Value[0],3) as int) as PatientAge, meta:['00100040'].Value[0] PatientSex, try_cast(try_to_timestamp(meta:['00080020'].Value[0],"yyyyMMdd") as Date) as StudyDate, meta:['00080030'].Value[0] StudyTime, meta:['00080050'].Value[0] AccessionNumber, meta:['00080060'].Value[0] Modality, meta:['00080008'].Value[0] ImageType, meta:['00180015'].Value[0] BodyPartExamined, meta:['00181030'].Value[0] ProtocolName, meta:['00080070'].Value[0] Manufacturer, meta:['00080080'].Value[0] InstitutionName, meta:['00080081'].Value[0] InstitutionAddress, meta:['0018700A'].Value[0] DetectorManufacturerName, meta:['0018700B'].Value[0] DetectorManufacturersModelName, meta:['00189024'].Value[0] MRTransmitCoilManufacturerName, meta:['00189025'].Value[0] ReceiveCoilManufacturerName, meta:['00120063'].Value[0] DeidentificationMethod, meta:['0008001C'].Value[0] SyntheticData, meta:['00120064'].Value[0] CodingSchemeVersion, meta:['00282110'].Value[0] LossyImageCompression, meta:['00131010'].Value[0] Creator, max(modificationTime) modificationTime, count(distinct path) num_files, avg(length) as avg_length, sum(length) length FROM identifier(:table) GROUP BY ALL ORDER BY StudyInstanceUID ) SELECT concat('view') as url ,* FROM base

datasets.name: 9651ec0b
queryLines:
-- object catalogs
select concat(table_catalog, '.', table_schema, '.', table_name) as table
from system.information_schema.tables where table_name = 'object_catalog'

datasets.name: c2b374ba
queryLines:
-- Pixel Models
SELECT entity_name, served_entity_name, max(entity_version) entity_version, custom_model_config.*, max(change_time) change_time
FROM system.serving.served_entities 
where entity_name like '%pixels%'
and endpoint_delete_time is null
GROUP BY ALL
order by change_time desc

lines:
# Pixels Medical Imaging summary dashboard

Based on DICOM files that have been acquired, unzipped, ingested and parsed using the Pixels Solution Accelerator
- Select the Object Catalog table of your choosing
- Select your OHIF viewer app hostname
- Use barcharts and histograms to narrow selection of SeriesInstanceUIDs
- Use **view** link on bottom table to view SeriesInstances
Data associated with the file rather than the contents of the header
